name: StableIschemicHeartDisease
title: Stable Ischemic Heart Disease
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to stable ischemic heart disease (SIHD).),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes atherosclerotic coronary artery disease such as recent-onset or stable angina. It also includes combination terms (e.g., Angina co-occurrent and due to arteriosclerosis of coronary artery bypass graft).),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes coronary artery thrombosis, coronary occlusion without specification of etiology, acute coronary syndrome (e.g., unstable angina, myocardial infarction) and other complications of coronary artery disease (e.g., ischemic cardiomyopathy).)
